summary: This mod aims to build much more on to Castle Volkihar and make it a suitable player home, it is a work in progress but still improves the castle main hall a great deal.
descriptionHtml:
This mod aims to build much more on to Castle Volkihar and make it a suitable player home, it is a work in progress but still improves the castle main hall a great deal.

so far it cleans up all the rubble in the main hall but in future versions I will add respawning blood barrels clean the cathedral and courtyard up and so on.

I also plan to make the previously ruined towers livable as well

have fun and enjoy :)
author: Darknessofchaos357
